"title": "4424: cedar",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "4424: cedar",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>A tall, majestic tree, native to Lebanon. In OT times it was highly prized for its wood, which was used extensively in the construction of Solomon's temple.</p>\n<h2>Cedar trees associated with Lebanon</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs4:33\">1KI 4:33</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg9:15\">JDG 9:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs14:9\">2KI 14:9</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr25:18\">2CH 25:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs19:23\">2KI 19:23</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa37:24\">ISA 37:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps29:5\">PSA 29:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps92:12\">PSA 92:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps104:16\">PSA 104:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song5:15\">SNG 5:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa14:8\">ISA 14:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer22:23\">JER 22:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek27:5\">EZK 27:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos14:5-Hos14:6\">HOS 14:5–14:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech11:1-Zech11:2\">ZEC 11:1–11:2</a></p>\n<h2>The cedar as a tall, majestic tree</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek31:3\">EZK 31:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job40:17\">JOB 40:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps80:10\">PSA 80:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa2:12-Isa2:13\">ISA 2:12–2:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek17:22-Ezek17:23\">EZK 17:22–17:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek31:7-Ezek31:8\">EZK 31:7–31:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos2:9\">AMO 2:9</a></p>\n<h2>Cedar trees indicating a fertile, well-watered land</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num24:5-Num24:6\">NUM 24:5–24:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps92:12-Ps92:15\">PSA 92:12–92:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa41:17-Isa41:20\">ISA 41:17–41:20</a></p>\n<h2>Cedar used allegorically</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek17:1-Ezek17:4\">EZK 17:1–17:4</a> <em>prophecy of a Davidic king being taken into captivity</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek17:22-Ezek17:23\">EZK 17:22–17:23</a> <em>prophecy of the Messiah coming from David's family</em></p>\n<h2>Cedar as a costly and valued wood</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs10:27\">1KI 10:27</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr1:15\">2CH 1:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr9:27\">2CH 9:27</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song8:8-Song8:9\">SNG 8:8–8:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa9:8-Isa9:10\">ISA 9:8–9:10</a></p>\n<h2>Cedar wood used in ritual purification</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev14:48-Lev14:53\">LEV 14:48–14:53</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev14:1-Lev14:7\">LEV 14:1–14:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num19:1-Num19:6\">NUM 19:1–19:6</a></p>\n<h2>Cedar wood imported from the north</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra3:7\">EZR 3:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam5:11\">2SA 5:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs5:1-1Kgs5:11\">1KI 5:1–5:11</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr2:3-2Chr2:16\">2CH 2:3–2:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs9:11\">1KI 9:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr22:4\">1CH 22:4</a></p>\n<h2>Cedar wood used in the construction of buildings</h2>\n<h3>Royal palaces and great houses</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:2-1Kgs7:3\">1KI 7:2–7:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam5:11\">2SA 5:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam7:2\">2SA 7:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:7\">1KI 7:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:11-1Kgs7:12\">1KI 7:11–7:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song1:17\">SNG 1:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer22:11-Jer22:15\">JER 22:11–22:15</a></p>\n<h3>The temple</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs6:18\">1KI 6:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam7:7\">2SA 7:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs6:9-1Kgs6:10\">1KI 6:9–6:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs6:20\">1KI 6:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs6:36\">1KI 6:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:12\">1KI 7:12</a></p>",
